  "formulaSource": "Base project cost ranges from HomeAdvisor and Angi 2025-2026 national average surveys for ADA and aging-in-place remodeling. Mobility level multipliers from NAHB Aging-in-Place Specialist (CAPS) program cost data 2025. Add-on costs for bathroom modifications, doorway widening, and flooring changes from HomeAdvisor cost surveys. Labor portion set at 45% of base project cost per NAHB renovation labor data. Regional labor multipliers derived from BLS Occupational Employment and Wage Statistics for construction and remodeling trades.",
